elopment for nearly a decade.</p> </div></section> <div id="respond" class="comment-respond"> <h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Leave a Reply <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/web-development/marketing/5-steps-to-twitter-success/#respond" style="display:none;">Cancel reply</a></small></h3> <div id="commentform" class="comment-form"> <iframe src="http://jetpack.wordpress.com/jetpack-comment/?blogid=13338603&#038;postid=972&#038;comment_registration=0&#038;require_name_email=1&#038;stc_enabled=1&#038;stb_enabled=1&#038;show_avatars=1&#038;avatar_default=mystery&#038;greeting=Leave+a+Reply&#038;greeting_reply=Leave+a+Reply+to+%25s&#038;color_scheme=light&#038;lang=en-US&#038;jetpack_version=3.0.2&#038;sig=edbcf58197de69f0a38e544145e923eca9d0abc4#parent=http%3A%2F%2Fjournalxtra.com%2Fweb-development%2Fmarketing%2F5-steps-to-twitter-success%2F" allowtransparency="false" style="width:100%; height: 430px;border:0px;" frameBorder="0" scrolling="no" name="jetpack_remote_comment" id="jetpack_remote_comment"></iframe> </div> </div> <input type="hidden" name="comment_parent" id="comment_parent" value=""/> <img src="http://journalxtra.com/wp-content/themes/dynamik-gen/images/content-filler.png" class="dynamik-content-filler-img"></main><aside class="sidebar sidebar-primary widget-area" role="complementary" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/WPSideBar"><section id="transposh-2" class="widget widget_transposh"><div class="widget-wrap"><h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">Read in Your Language</h4> <span class="no_translate"><select style="width:100%" name="lang" class="tp_lang2" onchange="document.location.href=this.options[this.selectedIndex].value;"><option value="/web-development/marketing/5-steps-to-twitter-success/" data-flag="us" data-lang="English" selected="selected">English</option><option value="/da/web-development/marketing/5-steps-to-twitter-success/" data-flag="dk" data-lang="Danish">Dansk</option><option valu